Definition: amnesia about particular events that is very convenient for the person who cannot remember
Example: why do politicians always develop selective amnesia when questioned about their transgressions?
Synonyms: amnesia, about, particular, events, that, is, very, convenient, for, the, person, who, cannot, remember, why, do, politicians, always, develop, selective, when, questioned, their, transgressions
Category: noun.cognition
